<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1010.58759.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Joculator problematicus Albano & Steger, sp. nov., holotype, NHMW-MO- 113580, Ashqelon, Israel, HELM project (sample S 58 _ 3 F): front (A, B), left side (C), right side (D, E) and back (F) views, protoconch (G, H), microsculpture (I) and base and siphonal canal (J). Scale bars: 0.5 mm (A-F); 0.2 mm (G, H); 0.3 mm (I); 0.4 mm (J)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/496964" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

